{
  "texts": [
    "It is entirely possible that good prompts to RNN models do not mean additional restrictions, but should simply be constructed using completely different guidelines.",
    "The authors of the aforementioned paper (Kocoń et al., 2023) foot_3 perform chain-of-thought to improve results on the MathQA dataset.",
    "Even including this approach, the Raven model achieved a very low accuracy of 5.43%.",
    "Without it, the model performed even worse, performing only very basic and simple calculations and achieving 4.13% accuracy.",
    "Raven struggled with questions that required intermediate results."
  ]
}